etera mutual pension insurance company asset management arm private company information  bloomberg july    pm et capital markets company overview of etera mutual pension insurance company asset management arm snapshot people company overview etera mutual pension insurance company asset management arm is a privately owned investment manager the firm primarily provides its services to small and medium sized entrepreneurs it manages separate clientfocused equity and fixed income portfolios the firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe it also invests in participations real estate loan receivable and other money market instruments and deposits the firm employs active portfolio management to make its investments it makes its bond investments through euro area government bonds and corporate loans the firm obtains external research to compliment its inhouse research it operates as a subsi etera mutual pension insurance company asset management arm is a privately owned investment manager the firm primarily provides its services to small and medium sized entrepreneurs it manages separate clientfocused equity and fixed income portfolios the firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe it also invests in participations real estate loan receivable and other money market instruments and deposits the firm employs active portfolio management to make its investments it makes its bond investments through euro area government bonds and corporate loans the firm obtains external research to compliment its inhouse research it operates as a subsidiary of etera mutual pension insurance company etera mutual pension insurance company asset management arm is based in helsinki finland detailed description palkkatilanportti helsinki  finland phone    wwweterafieneterainbriefeteraasaninvestoretusivuhtm key executives for etera mutual pension insurance company asset management arm ms johanna haukkovaara head of investment administr