puty ceo of etera will become deputy ceo of ilmarinen related articles  germans require education on pensions – fidelity  the year in pensions  industry responds to eiopa consultation latest news headlines your browser does not support html video adam cadle provides a summary of the big european pensions stories to have hit the headlines this month most read stories  irish nuj accepts decision to continue pension contributions to inm schemes  european commission reveals plans for crossborder pension product active investing does not lead to higher returns  dutch research  norway maintains top ranking in global retirement index eight out of top  from western europe   abp invests €m in infrastructure half of dutch population does not save for retirement norwegian govt pension fund global purchases washington dc property dutch manual labourers increasingly unable to work until retirement world markets  minute time delay ftse    nikkei    sp    crude oil na na this website is a part of perspective publishing limited registered in england no  by using this website you agree to our cookie policy and privacy policy etera mutual pension insurance appoints state street home asset tables service matrix providers surveys news events markets buyers guide glossary about us subscriptions   itemsview basket etera mutual pension insurance appoints state streetetera mutual pension insurance appoints state street february   february   state street reports its appointment by etera mutual pension insurance company etera of finland to provide a wide range of pension fund solutionsstate street will provide custody fund accounting transaction management securities lending futures clearing agent fund trading daily risk services otc derivatives servicing and collateral management for more than eur  billion in assets under managementgiven the finnish and european regulatory challenges facing the industry and our enhanced investment strategy we needed to look to future proof our current busin